# Project Directory for PROJ-363
# This directory serves as the root for the "Predicting the Impact of Additive Manufacturing Parameters on the Porosity of 316L Stainless Steel" project.
# Subdirectories (code/, data/, tests/, models/, results/, specs/, state/) are created by subsequent tasks (e.g., T001a logic applied here, T002, T006).
#
# Structure:
# ├── code/          # Python source modules
# ├── data/          # Raw and processed datasets
# ├── models/        # Trained model artifacts
# ├── results/       # Reports and plots
# ├── specs/         # Feature specifications
# ├── tests/         # Unit and contract tests
# ├── state/         # Artifact versioning state
# ├── requirements.txt
# └── .gitkeep